---
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const siteUrl = 'https://moncada25.github.io/fun-phone-web/roadmap/';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" x-data="pageState()" x-on:lang.window="updateLang($event.detail)" x-bind:lang="lang" class="scroll-smooth">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Roadmap Fun Phone | Próximas versiones, metas y visión</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Descubre hacia dónde va Fun Phone: objetivos de crecimiento, mejoras de calidad y nuevas funciones planificadas." />
    <link rel="canonical" href={siteUrl} />
    <link rel="alternate" href={siteUrl} hrefLang="es" />
    <link rel="alternate" href={siteUrl} hrefLang="en" />
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
    <meta property="og:type" content="article" />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="Fun Phone" />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Roadmap Fun Phone" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Metas de crecimiento y funciones en camino para Fun Phone." />
    <meta property="og:url" content={siteUrl} />
    <meta property="og:image" content={import.meta.env.BASE_URL + 'assets/screenshots/dialer.png'} />
    <meta property="og:locale" content="es_ES" />
    <meta property="og:locale:alternate" content="en_US" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href={import.meta.env.BASE_URL + 'assets/logo.png'} />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href={import.meta.env.BASE_URL + 'assets/logo.png'} />
    <script>
      const prefersDark = window.matchMedia && window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches;
      const savedTheme = localStorage.getItem('darkMode');
      const isDark = savedTheme !== null ? savedTheme === 'true' : prefersDark;
      document.documentElement.classList.toggle('dark', isDark);
      document.documentElement.style.colorScheme = isDark ? 'dark' : 'light';
    </script>
    <script defer src="https://unpkg.com/alpinejs@3.x.x/dist/cdn.min.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-sky-50/40 to-white text-neutral-900 dark:from-neutral-950 dark:via-neutral-950/50 dark:to-neutral-950">
    <Navbar />
    <main id="main-content" role="main" class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-6xl flex-col gap-16 px-4 pt-28 pb-20">
      <header class="rounded-4xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white/80 p-10 text-center shadow-xl shadow-accent/10 backdrop-blur dark:border-neutral-800 dark:bg-neutral-900/80">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-accent" x-show="lang==='es'">Visión y camino</p>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-accent" x-show="lang==='en'">Vision & path</p>
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-black leading-tight tracking-tight text-neutral-900 dark:text-accent">
          <span x-show="lang==='es'">Roadmap de Fun Phone</span>
          <span x-show="lang==='en'">Fun Phone roadmap</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300" x-show="lang==='es'">
          Proyectamos crecimiento, adopción y nuevas funciones manteniendo una filosofía local‑first y privacidad real.
        </p>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300" x-show="lang==='en'">
          We’re projecting growth, adoption, and new features while staying local‑first and privacy‑respecting.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">
          <span class="rounded-full border border-neutral-200 px-4 py-1 dark:border-neutral-700">Android 9+</span>
          <span class="rounded-full border border-neutral-200 px-4 py-1 dark:border-neutral-700">Local‑first</span>
          <span class="rounded-full border border-neutral-200 px-4 py-1 dark:border-neutral-700">Sin anuncios</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="space-y-3 rounded-3xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white/80 p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-neutral-800 dark:bg-neutral-900/70">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-accent">Now</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>T9 aún más rápido y preciso.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Notas: plantillas y fijar a contacto.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Gestor de contraseñas: generación avanzada y mejoras de UX.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Utilidades QR: historial y escaneo desde galería mejorado.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Rendimiento: inicio &lt; 2s y animaciones fluidas.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="space-y-3 rounded-3xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white/80 p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-neutral-800 dark:bg-neutral-900/70">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-accent">Next</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Widgets: favoritos, notas rápidas y marcación.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Accesibilidad: tamaño de fuente + alto contraste.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Calendario de festivos: más países y filtros.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Dedupe avanzado con sugerencias de fusión.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Juegos: skins y marcadores locales.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="space-y-3 rounded-3xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white/80 p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-neutral-800 dark:bg-neutral-900/70">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-accent">Later</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Analíticas de llamadas en dispositivo (duración, ratio, tendencias).</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Temas: más fuentes, paletas y animaciones.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Multi‑idioma: PT‑BR, FR.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Respuestas rápidas y rutinas tras llamada.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Backups cifrados bajo tu control.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_320px]">
        <article class="space-y-6 rounded-4xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white/80 p-8 shadow-lg shadow-accent/5 backdrop-blur dark:border-neutral-800 dark:bg-neutral-900/70">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-accent" x-show="lang==='es'">Temas estratégicos</h2>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-accent" x-show="lang==='en'">Strategic themes</h2>
          <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="rounded-3xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white/70 p-5 dark:border-neutral-800 dark:bg-neutral-900/60">
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-accent">Crecimiento y adopción</h3>
              <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>10k+ instalaciones con calificación ≥ 4.6.</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Mejor onboarding y guías interactivas.</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Traducciones y soporte a más regiones.</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-3xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white/70 p-5 dark:border-neutral-800 dark:bg-neutral-900/60">
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-accent">Calidad y estabilidad</h3>
              <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>99.5% sesiones libre de fallos.</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Pruebas de rendimiento en listas grandes.</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Mejores migraciones y respaldo local.</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-3xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white/70 p-5 dark:border-neutral-800 dark:bg-neutral-900/60 md:col-span-2">
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-accent">Funcionalidad</h3>
              <ul class="mt-2 grid gap-y-1 text-sm text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 sm:grid-cols-2">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Contactos avanzados: etiquetas y lotes.</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Suite de productividad más flexible.</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Mini‑juegos con nuevas temáticas.</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Utilidades QR y festivos ampliadas.</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <aside class="space-y-4 rounded-4xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white/80 p-6 text-sm text-neutral-700 shadow-lg shadow-accent/5 backdrop-blur dark:border-neutral-800 dark:bg-neutral-900/70 dark:text-neutral-300">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">Preguntas y feedback</h2>
          <p x-show="lang==='es'">¿Tienes ideas o quieres priorizar algo? Escribe a <a href="mailto:santiago.moncada.dev@gmail.com" class="text-accent underline">santiago.moncada.dev@gmail.com</a>.</p>
          <p x-show="lang==='en'">Got ideas or priorities? Email <a href="mailto:santiago.moncada.dev@gmail.com" class="text-accent underline">santiago.moncada.dev@gmail.com</a>.</p>
          <a href={import.meta.env.BASE_URL + 'features/'} class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-accent/30 px-4 py-2 font-semibold text-accent transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-accent hover:bg-accent/10 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent">
            <span x-show="lang==='es'">Ver funciones actuales</span>
            <span x-show="lang==='en'">See current features</span>
          </a>
        </aside>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />

    <script is:inline>
      function pageState() {
        return {
          lang: localStorage.getItem('lang') || (navigator.language?.startsWith('es') ? 'es' : 'en'),
          init() {
            document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-lang', this.lang);
          },
          updateLang(value) {
            if (!value) return;
            this.lang = value;
            document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-lang', this.lang);
          }
        };
      }
    </script>
  </body>
  </html>
